title: Book of Dead
description: Book of Dead is a 5-reel video slot game. Up to 10 lines can be activated, lines are numbered and always activated in numerical order (1, 2, 3, 4, etc.).

title: Rise of Olympus
description:
Unleash the power of the gods in the latest entertaining Play'n GO slot, Rise of Olympus! Join the mighty Greek gods in a quest for riches and prosperity in this all new 5x5 grid slot.

Make winning combinations by matching 3 symbols or more in a row horizontally or vertically. Winning combos will also disappear and be replaced by new symbols, making it possible to pick up even more wins from a single spin.

title: Scroll of Dead
description:
SCROLL OF DEAD is a 6-reel, 3-row video slot game with 10 paylines.

In the base game the 6th reel is locked. 3 or more SCATTER symbols on any reel trigger FREE SPIN mode with an additional 6th reel, and an initial 8 spins. When FREE SPIN starts a random symbol is chosen to become a special expanding symbol!

The chosen symbol can form winning combinations across non-adjacent reels. When a winning combination is formed, then all chosen symbols expand.

title: Fire Joker
description: The reels can set fire at any moment in Fire Joker, a 3-reel video slot game from Play’n GO. Things can get a little heated when a combination of three matching symbols align in any horizontal or diagonal pay line

title: Legacy of Egypt
description: Experience the divine magic and mysticism that has been exalted along the Nile since ancient times in Legacy of Egypt, a 5-reel slot from Play'n GO. Your goal is to line up symbols depicting Cleopatra, Anubis and other dynasties and deities. The sacred scarab beetle is wild and can crawl in to help you create even more winning combinations along any of the game's 30 lines. Any three pyramid symbols scattered about the reels set the Wheel of the Gods spinning. When it stops, the Wheel grants you a sequence of up to 20 free spins, on which every prize-winning combination is worth double or up to 10 times the normal amount! Any two or three wild scarabs that appear on a free spin inject several special Pyramid Spins into your free-spin sequence to boost your winnings even further. You can even trigger an extra free-spin sequence if you can harness the power of the pyramids. Experience the beauty and benevolence of the greats and gods of the past in Legacy of Egypt!

title: Rich Wilde and the Tome of Madness
description:
Rich Wilde has returned! Everybody’s favourite hero is back for another adventure in the latest Play’n GO title, Rich Wilde and the Tome of Madness!

Follow our intrepid explorer as he embarks on an epic quest to unlock the secrets of the sinister Cult of Cthulhu. Join him in the hunt for ancient relics and artefacts as you try to reveal the mysterious occult forces at work, and search for the legendary Book of Madness.

title: Reactoonz
description: Round up energetic extraterrestrials in the Reactoonz slot from Play'nGO. Like its prequel Energoonz, Reactoonz is a playful parallel universe charged with stellar power and prizes. Highly animated aliens drop from the heavens and land to occupy the 7x7 game grid. Win a prize for each cluster of 5 or more aliens of the same race: The larger your cluster, the greater your profit! The flux capacitors essentially serve as wild symbols to help you win more. Aliens in winning clusters are instantly teleported away to be replaced by new space invaders from above, giving you multiple chances to win in the same round. Try to make contact with oversized aliens! They can multiply your prize when they become part of a winning cluster.

title: The Sword and The Grail
description: Step back in time and travel to the legendary court of King Arthur in our latest fantastic new slot The Sword and The Grail!This 5-reel slot gives players the chance to multiply their winning lines by 100! King Arthur, Lady Guinevere, Sir Lancelot and Merlin serve as the HP symbols in the game (the LP symbols are represented by 10 through Ace), and players have to match 3 or more symbols across the twenty paylines to pick up a standard base game win.The mythical Holy Grail stands as the game's Wild and can substitute for any of the game's symbols (excluding the Scatter). In the base game, the Wild can appear with a Multiplier attached and, if it forms part of a winning combination it will multiply the win!The Scatter symbol is Excalibur, the infamous sword in the stone that made Arthur king. Three swords on the reels will trigger the game's Free Spin feature, granting players an initial five free spins. The aim of the feature is to collect more swordges, transforming yourself from a lowly squire to the King of Knights!Each stage can be unlocked by collecting a certain number of swords and reaching a new stage will grant the player and an additional five free spins and will transform the Wild into a Multiplier, starting with a x2 Multiplier in the first stage.Stage 2 is unlocked by collecting six swords in total, and any Wilds will multiply winning lines by x5.Stage 3 is unlocked by collecting 11 swords in total, and any Wilds will multiply winning lines by x10The final stage will be unlocked by collecting 18 swords in total, and the Multiplier Wild will be set at x100!Glory and honour await those brave enough to take up the challenge of The Sword and The Grail!

title: Rise of Merlin
description: Rise of Merlin is a 5-reel video slot game. An additional special Expanding Symbol is chosen at random.

title: Moon Princess
description: Harness girl power to win in Moon Princess, an action-packed video slot from Play'n GO graced by the lunar loveliness of the powerful princess trio: Love, Star and Storm. Connect three or more matching symbols horizontally or vertically in the 5 x 5 grid to win. Symbols in winning combos disappear, allowing symbols in the same column to drop into place to give you new chances to win on each spin. Each time new symbols drop, the factor that multiplies your prize increases! The Wild Moon may appear in place of the middle symbol in a winning combo to help you win on the next drop by substituting for other game symbols.

title: Free Reelin' Joker
description:
Free Reelin’ Joker is a 3-reel video slot with 1 payline. The game initially has 3 reels. Activating the FREE REELIN' FUN feature adds an additional reel. Up to 3 additional reels can be added in total.

title: Reactoonz 2
description:
Reactoonz 2 is a 7x7 cascading video slot game.

Wins are achieved by getting 5 or more symbols in clusters. These are removed and new symbols fill up the grid. Cascades continue until no more wins can be created.

A random one-eyed symbol type fluctuates on each new round. If fluctuating symbols form a winning cluster, a single ELECTRIC WILD is created randomly on any spot of the removed symbols. Furthermore, FLUCTOMETER collects all the removed fluctuating symbols and creates 1, 2 or 3 ELECTRIC WILDS randomly when full, after all wins and cascades play out.

title: The Green Knight
description:
The Green Knight is a 5-Reel Video Slot with 20-fixed paylines.

The Green Knight symbol can land on ANY reel; 3 or more triggers 5 Free Spins. The Shield is Wild and can land on ANY reel; this symbol substitutes for all other symbols except The Green Knight and the Special Green Knight symbol.

title: Honey Rush

title: Prism of Gems
description:
PRISM OF GEMS is a 5-reel Dynamic Payways video slot machine with up to 3087 ways to win!

There are 5 vertical reels and 1 horizontal reel (MULTIPLIER REEL). Winning combinations are removed. New symbols cascade into view to re-fill the empty positions to potentially form new wins. The process is repeated if new wins are continually being created. Only the highest winning combination per symbol is paid.

title: Rich Wilde and the Amulet of the Dead
description:
Rich Wilde and the Amulet of Dead is a 5x3-reel video slot game with up to 10 paylines.

The pendant is a SCATTER and can appear on ANY reel. The pendant is also a WILD SCATTER and can substitute for any other symbol (except for special EXPANDING SYMBOL) to form a winning combination. SCATTER wins are multiplied by the total bet staked and are added to the payline wins.
THOTH WILD appears on reels 2, 3 and 4 only. THOTH WILD can appear as a stack and will trigger THOTH MULTIPLIER.

title: Dawn of Egypt
description: Dawn of Egypt is a 5-Reel Video Slot machine with 10 fixed paylines. title: Wild Frames
description: Wild Frames is a 7x7 cascading video slot game.Wins are achieved by getting 5 or more symbols in clusters. These are removed, and new symbols fill up the grid. Cascades continue until no more wins can be created. On a non-winning spin, there is the chance to add 4-6 wild symbols randomly.Wild symbols create a sticky frame on all the grid positions they land on and upgrade existing frames with win multipliers! However, all frames stay inactive until Wild Frames feature is triggered.All winning symbols fill the Charge Meter, each adds 1 charge. 20, 40 and 60 charges activate Transform, Wildcard and Shatter features. Transform turns all non-suit symbols into one type of non-suit symbol, Wildcard randomly places 3-6 wilds and Shatter removes all suit symbols.Wild Frames feature triggers if the Charge Meter is fully charged with 80 symbols. It can be overcharged every additional 10 charges add 2 frames at random. All symbols under frames turn into wild symbols and all frames become active. For each winning cluster, the highest win multiplier is used. Further charges do not have an effect after the activation happens!

title: Golden Ticket 2
description:
Enter a carnival of wonders in Golden Ticket 2! Join the Ringmaster and his amazing acts under the big top and make your fortune in the golden age of live entertainment.

Golden Ticket 2 is a 5x5 cascading gridslot with a 1920’s circus theme. The game’s biggest symbols are all represented by world-famous characters of the big top, the Ringmaster, a Knife-Thrower and a Clown.
